<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>249</hymn_number>
<author>Thangngur</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lei hi a ngui zo tai
 A chunga mihiem haw tawh
 Gitlohna leh gimtheih na'n a dim zo
 I mi ngaihum hawu leh,
 Guolpha a chieh zotau.

[V2]
 Aw Belam nunnem in,
 Gam thak, A va bawl chu;
 Aw, ka thagau nang le
 Zie gam nuom chu hawl in
 Khawvel pawtsan tienga
 Na umna mun dingin

[V3]
 2. Dikna gam a zo tau
 Aw, kumsawt gam lun ding chu
 Lei gimum hi albang in mang mahleh,
 Lal Krista na gin chun
 Gam thak ah leng inla.

[V4]
 3. Ma a pi leh pute'n
 A muh phak loh uh gam chu,
 Thisan zalin ken ka na mu ta ie,
 A zawtna lampi chu
 Lal Krista hi ahi.</lyrics>
<title>Belam No Munsiem</title>
</song>